Barbara knocked on the frame of the open door. A woman in green track suit answered, &ldquo;Whadya want?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Is this the Bernfield residence?&rdquo;
&ldquo;No.&rdquo; She paused. She was smoking a cigarette. No filter. Her iridescent green track suit had seen better days. &ldquo;This is the Bernstein residence.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Oh,&rdquo; said Barbara, trying to sound upbeat, as if she had heard good news. &ldquo;Well, I thought it was the Bernfield residence&hellip;.&rdquo;
